metadata.name: NEBULART #08
metadata.description:
This nebula is the result of a generative art process.

It is the result of the random and unpredictable nature of the Universe.

This explosion of pixels followed a series of partially random parameters which gave birth to this artwork.
It will therefore be impossible to recreate it again, which makes it unique.

I like to think that its beauty comes from the complexity of its creation process.
